data.title: Event Calendar
data.meta_description: Browse Lookout's Santa Cruz County public event calendar. This is your place to go for things to do in Santa Cruz County. Find all the concerts, plays, live music, pub crawls, family events, poetry slams, things to do with kids, things to do outdoors in and around Santa Cruz County and more.
